WEBVTT

00:00:01.446 --> 00:00:08.004
zayt zhe azoy gut, ir hot oyfgehert tsu dertseyln vi ir hot gekrign di ershte MAZKORET un ir hot geven tsufridn.

00:00:05.333 --> 00:00:09.478
yo, shtark tsufridn.

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:10.029
vos zhe geshet vayter?

00:00:09.563 --> 00:00:17.859
nu, bin ikh aheymgekumen, ikh hob gekoyft a DUD CHASHMAL fun zekhtsik liter, koydem ikh zol mir kenen bodn di tsvey sheyne kinder.

00:00:17.933 --> 00:00:23.445
dos iz geven dos ershte. nokh dem ho- ho- hob ikh gebroykht tsoln dire-gelt do oyf UNK.

00:00:23.991 --> 00:00:31.261
dos tsoln un s'iz gevaksn der indeks, hot men azoy geven azoy nervez, az Sanek er nebekh hot zeyer veynik,

00:00:31.261 --> 00:00:35.817
er hot gegan tsu an andern arbet, un er hot gebiglt, s'iz im shlekht gevorn, s'a,

00:00:35.817 --> 00:00:38.463
ikh hob gehat mit im nebekh tsores a sakh.

00:00:38.520 --> 00:00:39.183
shoyn.

00:00:39.183 --> 00:00:40.471
in di kinder,

00:00:40.545 --> 00:00:44.608
zenen gegan in shul, un nokh dem hobn zey ongehoybn arbetn.

00:00:44.608 --> 00:00:47.545
un dos yingl hot gelernt in Tel Aviv,

00:00:47.545 --> 00:00:49.899
far a, ikh bin gekumen fun a

00:00:49.899 --> 00:00:53.127
vi azoy heyst es der

00:00:53.590 --> 00:00:56.587
nu, m'hot gemakht HAZAKARA,

00:00:57.589 --> 00:01:13.676
der Sigetern un ikh hob mitgenumen mayn zun oykh. tsurikkumendik s'geven in a donershtik, a klal, ze'mir gekumen, iz a hint oyf der TAKHANA iz geven a shtikl KONDITORIA, un ze'mir ahin arayn, ikh vel dir a koyf ton a kleyn ROLLekhl,

00:01:13.676 --> 00:01:17.344
ikh zol hobn oyf shabes, vayl ikh hob nisht gehat ven tsu makhn gornisht.

00:01:17.805 --> 00:01:19.776
kum arayn ahin,

00:01:19.776 --> 00:01:28.059
mayn yingl kukt aher un kukt ahin un s'gefelt im. zog ikh efsher nemt ir on dos yingl far a ir zolt im oyslernen a beker?

00:01:28.369 --> 00:01:33.931
zogt er, dos yingl gefelt mir, zogt er, zeyer. s'geven -za aza sheyn kind az az nisht poshet.

00:01:35.473 --> 00:01:37.458
ir meynt az er nisht geblibn?

00:01:37.549 --> 00:01:42.583
er iz geblibn. er hot gearbet dort, er iz avek nokh dem in Tel Aviv oyf a UNK

00:01:42.583 --> 00:01:43.688
bay eynem,

00:01:43.688 --> 00:01:51.397
un er iz dort gevezn, un do geven un dort geven, un a- mami, ikh vel avek forn fun do! m'hot im nisht genumen tsu di TZAVA,

00:01:51.859 --> 00:01:53.729
vayl ven ikh hob im gehat,

00:01:53.729 --> 00:01:55.315
hot er a tseykhn

00:01:55.315 --> 00:02:00.917
do ot ot, mit di tsvangen, hobn zey bahoyptet az dos iz epes a feler.

00:02:00.917 --> 00:02:04.846
dos yingl er iz geven sheyn un hoykh mit ale mayles,

00:02:05.005 --> 00:02:10.638
vu m'hot gebroykht geyn helfn iz er gelofn, far di vos zenen gegangen do er vil oykhet un

00:02:10.638 --> 00:02:14.161
s'hot im azoy barirt, far vos hot men im nisht genumen?

00:02:14.185 --> 00:02:16.477
der vayl far dem shnit do ot ot.

00:02:16.477 --> 00:02:19.894
s'zet zikh im on a bisl, ober ales voyl.

00:02:19.894 --> 00:02:25.974
shoyn er iz, un s'gekumen a meydl fun Amerike un er hot nisht gekukt tsi zi iz a dare tsi zi iz a,

00:02:26.858 --> 00:02:30.632
un un un s'iz gevorn un er iz avek un fun demolts on,

00:02:30.013 --> 00:02:31.964
ven iz er avekgeforn keyn Amerike?

00:02:31.583 --> 00:02:35.289
shoyn nokh far mayn UNK iz geshtorbn.

00:02:35.430 --> 00:02:37.738
befor mit tsvey epes, nokh in

00:02:37.738 --> 00:02:41.097
z- nayn un zekhtsik epes.

00:02:41.097 --> 00:02:42.141
epes azoy.

00:02:41.691 --> 00:02:43.608
ven iz ayer man geshtorbn?

00:02:43.442 --> 00:02:45.791
in tsvey un zibetsik.

00:02:46.635 --> 00:02:49.076
demolts blaybt ir bloyz mit di tokhter,

00:02:48.306 --> 00:02:54.369
bin ikh geblibn mit mayn tokhter. der tokhter iz geven in shul in Yerusholaim,

00:02:54.369 --> 00:02:56.872
un zi iz nokh gegangen in shul

00:02:57.418 --> 00:03:04.739
un hob ikh do shkheynim, ikh fleg araynkumen, un zi iz geven sheyn un zi iz geven a, zi hot gehat a gutn geshtal,

00:03:04.739 --> 00:03:09.444
un tsu di yene shkheynim zenen ge- iz gekumen der der khosn,

00:03:09.467 --> 00:03:13.629
un er hot zi eyn mol derzen un un er hot gezogt,

00:03:13.838 --> 00:03:16.431
er vil zikh mit ir bakant makhn.

00:03:17.702 --> 00:03:21.858
un ikh gey aroys, ruft zikh on di shokhnte vu er iz geven,

00:03:21.858 --> 00:03:28.310
"du Riki, hostu a mazl vos a yingl s'vil zikh bakant makhn mit dayn Estern!"

00:03:28.823 --> 00:03:30.456
ikh kuk ir,

00:03:30.456 --> 00:03:33.035
kuk zi on, ikh hob nisht gevust.

00:03:33.295 --> 00:03:40.902
er iz gekumen, er hot geredt, er hot gezen ober nisht keyn negideste, mayn man iz geven nebekh zeyer in a shlekhtn MATZAV krank,

00:03:40.902 --> 00:03:42.167
nisht poshet,

00:03:42.167 --> 00:03:52.234
er iz fun a balebatishe shtub geven un a negidishe shtub, ober gezunt iz bay got, un dort hot zikh oykh gemakht der nokh di mame iz nisht gezunt.

00:03:52.234 --> 00:04:08.642
shoyn, zi hot khasene gehat un er hot nisht gevolt blaybn do, nor geyn aheym keyn London, un in London hot er zikh zayn postn un dort iz er in der heym, er hot zikh a yene sheyne dire un borekhashem fun ir hob ikh nakhes merer vi funem zun.

00:04:08.125 --> 00:04:10.349
biz velkhn yor hot ir gearbet?

00:04:10.349 --> 00:04:12.624
ir aleyn biz velkhn yor hot ir gea-

00:04:11.398 --> 00:04:17.048
ikh hob nokh gearbet un nokh dem iz geven a MAKHLAVA oyf Rekhov Ezre,

00:04:17.048 --> 00:04:25.570
iz geven a bulgar, hot zikh, fun Ramle, hot zikh arayngetsoygn in der MACHLAVA a shtikl plats,

00:04:25.570 --> 00:04:28.082
er hot gemakht di gezaltsene kez.

00:04:28.425 --> 00:04:31.206
un der hot gemakht dem yagurt,

00:04:31.206 --> 00:04:36.024
m'hot gebroykht vashn di sh- di kestlekh un di shislekh, m'hot tsurikgebrengt

00:04:36.024 --> 00:04:38.345
un di KONDIRES fun di milkh,

00:04:38.345 --> 00:04:44.198
ikh hob mikh mit dem oykhet opgedreyt, ober der bal- der iz geven shtark a guter balbos.

00:04:44.659 --> 00:04:46.807
a harts, ober er hot gezogt,

00:04:46.807 --> 00:04:49.490
Ritele, zey hobn mikh azoy gerufn,

00:04:49.490 --> 00:05:00.516
du host goldene hent un du makhst un du tust. ikh hob mikh zeyer shtark geflayst, mit shtivl ongeton, mit a shurts, mit oysgeveykte hent, ikh fleg aheymkumen ikh hob mikh nisht getoygt rirn.

00:05:00.808 --> 00:05:02.844
ober ikh hob gemuzt.

00:05:02.968 --> 00:05:05.847
nu, dos iz ober nor geven a sezon arbet.

00:05:06.276 --> 00:05:10.955
dray fir khadoshim iz geven der milkh vos er hot genitst,

00:05:10.955 --> 00:05:21.659
un nokh er hot mir gegebn ale mol ven ikh hob geendikt hot er mir gegebn merer mit a bisl gelt, un ikh hob genumen dos gelt in arayngetrogn in Tel Aviv un batsolt di shtub.

00:05:23.640 --> 00:05:25.203
dos hob ikh getun.

00:05:26.661 --> 00:05:29.945
iz bi- nokh dem hot ir nokh gearbet ergets?

00:05:29.192 --> 00:05:37.592
nokh dem bin ikh krank gevorn, neyn neyn neyn, m'hot gedarft aropnemen a brust, ikh hob finef NITUCHIM oyf mir, finef shtik!

00:05:37.592 --> 00:05:40.976
azoy vi ir kukt mikh on bin ikh tsefidlt in gantsn.

00:05:40.976 --> 00:05:43.259
ober dos mol geyt mir nokh.

00:05:43.587 --> 00:05:45.606
ven s'geyt, ven nisht veyn ikh.

00:05:49.830 --> 00:05:53.283
ikh hob aykh gevolt fregn, ir dertseylt vegn di

00:05:53.830 --> 00:05:58.819
der yingl un di meydl, ir zent gekumen do zenen nokh geven kinder, ir zent gekumen do in land arayn,

00:05:56.648 --> 00:05:59.224
yo yo yo yo.

00:05:59.466 --> 00:06:02.694
ir zent a gelitene, ayer man hot geven a gelitener,

00:06:02.694 --> 00:06:09.248
di kinder hobn gefregt fragn, ir hot zey dertseylt vos ir hot alts adurkh gemeynt, di ale tsores, zey hobn zey hobn gevust vegn dem?

00:06:07.093 --> 00:06:18.055
zey hobn ge- zey hobn gehert fun dos. ober kinder geyen dokh um in droysn, un ir, zey hobn gehert az ikh bin geven in Oyshvits un s'geven, un zey, vos heyst zey zey veysn.

00:06:18.383 --> 00:06:23.476
i di tokhter veyst un i der zun, poshet di di tsveyte dor shoyn fun zey

00:06:23.476 --> 00:06:26.058
yene zenen shoyn mer ke-

00:06:26.058 --> 00:06:32.276
m'get dokh undz arayn in shul, zogt men dokh shoyn bay di goyim, zogt men shoyn az s'iz s'nisht geven.

00:06:32.276 --> 00:06:34.728
nu, vos ken men ton, vi azoy s'geven.

00:06:34.887 --> 00:06:37.159
kh'hob aykh gevolt nokh fregn a frage.

00:06:36.540 --> 00:06:38.272
nu, BEVAKASHA.

00:06:37.317 --> 00:06:41.006
ir hot adurkh gemakht azoy fil tsores, vos ir hot mir dertseylt.

00:06:39.223 --> 00:06:42.237
shtark a sakh, shtark a sakh.

00:06:41.586 --> 00:06:44.938
farloyrn a groyse teyl fun der mishpokhe,

00:06:44.809 --> 00:06:46.136
u ha! u ha!

00:06:48.437 --> 00:06:50.928
vi hot gevirkt oyf ayer lebn

00:06:51.002 --> 00:06:54.742
vos ir hot adurkh gemakht, vos gloybt ir, vi hot dos gevirkt oyf aykh?

00:06:55.390 --> 00:07:00.094
ikh veys vi azoy s'hot gevirkt, der fun oybn hot gevolt,

00:06:56.942 --> 00:06:58.269
vos gloybt ir?

00:07:00.094 --> 00:07:02.353
az di kinder zoln hobn a mame,

00:07:02.511 --> 00:07:06.977
un zol vayl zey hobn nebekh zeyer gikh ongevoyrn di dem tate,

00:07:07.152 --> 00:07:12.633
shtelt zikh for, finef un tsvontsik yor vert shoyn hitstert, zibetsn teg un elef, un elef.

00:07:12.633 --> 00:07:17.541
vayl m'hot hitst gebentsht, morgn iz reshkhoydesh, broykht men tseyln di teg un shikn tiken.

00:07:18.053 --> 00:07:20.328
un ikh geplogt.

00:07:20.328 --> 00:07:21.523
geplogt.

00:07:22.896 --> 00:07:29.538
un m'hot mir gegebn zeyer veynik BITUACH LEUMI, nisht poshet veynik, ikh hob nisht gehat vos m'broykh.

00:07:29.089 --> 00:07:31.496
ir hot gekrign epes fun di daytshn?

00:07:31.705 --> 00:07:32.959
hitstert.

00:07:32.959 --> 00:07:34.146
hersht hitst.

00:07:34.202 --> 00:07:35.478
tsvey yor.

00:07:36.042 --> 00:07:38.871
ober ikh hob nisht keyn gantse finef hundert mark.

00:07:40.007 --> 00:07:50.328
un ikh veys nisht fun vu mentshn redn az m'vet nor gebn finef yor. far vos zol men nor gebn finef yor? un di mentshn vos zey zenen shoyn do lenger,

00:07:50.588 --> 00:08:00.791
un bakumen fun di KIRYA di gantse tsayt, dos iz nisht keyn feler. nor undz kumt zikh nisht, ikh bin dokh shoyn do fun akht un fuftsik, ikh hob nokh nisht bakumen fun ergets gornisht.

00:08:01.455 --> 00:08:08.941
nu, tsi s'iz emes ikh veys nisht, ikh het avade gevolt m'zol gebn, un az m'vet nisht gebn vel ikh oykh zayn do.

00:08:07.665 --> 00:08:08.975
lo'mir hofn.

00:08:09.437 --> 00:08:11.996
zayt azoy gut, zogt mir,

00:08:12.897 --> 00:08:16.046
di ale yorn nokh dem vos ir hot adurkh gemakht

00:08:16.272 --> 00:08:20.791
pasirt a yor, ir hot epes sh- shvere khaloymes vegn di ale tsores,

00:08:20.791 --> 00:08:22.998
ir dermant zikh vegn dem alemen?

00:08:22.768 --> 00:08:24.685
ikh ikh kler tomed!

00:08:24.692 --> 00:08:29.866
ikh kler az s'mir shver gevezn, un fun ven on, vifl hob ikh mikh geplogt mit ABE.

00:08:29.890 --> 00:08:32.044
fun eyn shpitol in andern.

00:08:32.352 --> 00:08:34.493
do iz er geven Kfar Sava,

00:08:34.493 --> 00:08:37.252
do iz er geven in, in Bergzon,

00:08:37.252 --> 00:08:44.768
hitstert dray fir khadoshim, eyn mol ven m'hot im gemakht dem NITUACH oyfn kop, iz er geven elef teg BELI HAKARA!

00:08:46.107 --> 00:08:49.470
unter di elef teg fleg ikh tog un nakht

00:08:49.470 --> 00:08:52.209
l- geyn un kukn un nebekh un

00:08:52.671 --> 00:08:55.199
eyn mol, lozt men mikh arayn,

00:08:55.199 --> 00:08:59.510
un er tut a zog, ikh vil zayn a shatkhn farn ikh veys vemen.

00:08:59.510 --> 00:09:01.085
ikh hob im ongekukt,

00:09:01.176 --> 00:09:05.827
er hot nebekh geshlofn di gantse tsayt, ober bald hot er shoyn nisht gevust un,

00:09:06.019 --> 00:09:09.036
ober nokh dem iz er tsu zikh gekumen,

00:09:09.036 --> 00:09:11.227
ober s'hot nisht gedoyert tsu fil.

00:09:11.284 --> 00:09:16.796
un der profesor, Ashkenazi, vos er hot im operirt, er iz oykh nebekh geshtorbn.

00:09:18.625 --> 00:09:20.947
er hot gemakht a NITUACH oyfn kop.

00:09:24.430 --> 00:09:27.023
zogt mir, ikh hob ikh aykh gevolt fregn nokh a frage,

00:09:27.636 --> 00:09:41.889
ir dertseylt, zayendik in di lagern, nokh makhndik di ale tsores in di vagonen, in di dortn di tsores, mentshn hobn geshtorbn, nisht oysgehaltn, vos gloybt ir hot aykh perzenlekh geholfn adurkh tsu geyn dem gehenem.

00:09:41.912 --> 00:09:46.496
ikh ken aykh zogn efsher, ikh hob imer gehat a groysn vil,

00:09:47.059 --> 00:09:49.061
ikh hob mikh nisht gelozt.

00:09:50.670 --> 00:10:06.746
fun an arbet hob ikh mikh nisht gevert, ikh bin gegan in ale zaytn. vos m'hot mir gegebn iz geven hakl revekh,s'hot emetser a vorf geton a a a kotske tsuker, iz ober di di daytshn hobn geshturket, zey hobn nisht gelozt, di tsivil flegn veln a a gib ton.

00:10:07.107 --> 00:10:12.518
un un ikh hob mikh nisht gelozt, ikh hob imer gehat a groysn RATZON.

00:10:13.300 --> 00:10:14.813
zet ver ikh bin!

00:10:15.392 --> 00:10:16.466
KOL HAKAVOD!

00:10:17.282 --> 00:10:20.147
yetst volt ikh aykh gevolt fregn nokh a frage.

00:10:19.560 --> 00:10:21.208
nu, BEVAKASHA.

00:10:20.147 --> 00:10:23.097
beetsem nisht keyn frage, epes a gedank.

00:10:22.716 --> 00:10:23.537
nu.

00:10:24.167 --> 00:10:29.949
ven ayere kinder, ayere eyniklekh, ir hot dokh a tokhter un a zun, vifl eyniklekh hot ir?

00:10:29.617 --> 00:10:30.490
fir.

00:10:30.327 --> 00:10:33.746
fir eyniklekh, tsvey fun di tokhter un tsvey funem zun.

00:10:31.163 --> 00:10:33.890
yo, yo, yo.

00:10:34.343 --> 00:10:36.750
ven zey voltn aykh gefregt, mame,

00:10:37.212 --> 00:10:40.159
nokh dem vi du host adurkh gemakht dos ales,

00:10:39.726 --> 00:10:40.648
nu,

00:10:40.249 --> 00:10:42.757
vos far a eytse voltstu undz gezogt,

00:10:42.848 --> 00:10:49.406
az m'zol kenen oysmaydn azelkhe, dos yidishe folk zol kenen oysmaydn azelkhe tsores, vos volt ir zey gezogt far a eytse?

00:10:49.395 --> 00:10:58.282
hu! do- do- dos iz nisht gezogt gevorn vos ikh ken zogn, ober vos der fun oybn zol firn az s'zol shoyn nisht kumen tsu di tsores.

00:10:52.737 --> 00:10:54.233
vos volt ir ir gezogt?

00:10:58.440 --> 00:11:01.775
ir perzenlekh, hot ir zey, vos far a eytse volt ir zey gezogt?

00:11:01.765 --> 00:11:15.782
ikh hob nisht gezogt gornisht. ikh bin geshtanen, ikh hob nisht gezogt. vos, neyn, neyn, ne- ikh ho- neyn ikh ikh hob nisht gevust tsu zogn, ikh zog aykh zet ir, ikh red un red ober ho-, ikh hob gezogt, s'do a got in himl un s'zol mer nisht zayn azelkhes.

00:11:04.532 --> 00:11:07.597
ir hot nisht, ir hot ni- ir veyst nisht vos tsu zogn far UNK.

00:11:17.745 --> 00:11:22.953
iz epes dos vos ikh hob aykh nisht gefregt, ir hot gevolt epes tsugebn tsu ayer SIPUR vos ir hot mir yetst dertseylt?

00:11:21.694 --> 00:11:27.628
ne- ikh ikh meyn ikh hob aykh ales ge- vos ikh hob gehat in boykh hob ikh,

00:11:27.583 --> 00:11:29.866
hob ikh aykh gevolt biz yetst danken,

00:11:29.866 --> 00:11:33.466
yetst veln mir makhn a kurtsn iberrays, veln mir aribergeyn tsu di bilder.

00:11:33.895 --> 00:11:39.255
velkhe, deye? a- undzer? O- OKEY, OKEY, OKEY

00:11:34.553 --> 00:11:38.310
ikh vel aykh bald er- ikh vel aykh bald erklern vi m' vi s'vert gemakht.

00:11:41.556 --> 00:11:43.760
in mitn der bild,

00:11:43.834 --> 00:11:46.291
iz mayn bruder Yosi.

00:11:46.534 --> 00:11:52.099
makht er mir do dort khaveyrim zayne, mit di iz er avek in MUNKASZOLGALAT.

00:11:52.099 --> 00:11:53.734
un keyner iz nishto.

00:11:54.043 --> 00:11:55.150
leyder.

00:11:54.769 --> 00:11:57.733
vi arum hot ir, vi hot ir gekrign dos bild?

00:11:57.233 --> 00:12:00.129
dos bild hob ikh getrogn in der heym.

00:12:00.186 --> 00:12:02.036
nokh dem, nokhn bafrayen.

00:12:01.755 --> 00:12:02.997
yo, yo, yo.

00:12:04.101 --> 00:12:06.457
dos iz mayn shvester Honi.

00:12:06.767 --> 00:12:14.203
zi iz avek keyn Bergn Belzn un hot op geplogt di gantse tsayt, un farn bafrayen iz zi nebekh geshtorbn.

00:12:14.344 --> 00:12:17.257
ober zi iz geven nebekh a CHATICHA,

00:12:18.208 --> 00:12:19.079
UNK

00:12:18.900 --> 00:12:21.104
dos bild hot ir oykhet gefunen

00:12:20.757 --> 00:12:21.611
yo.

00:12:21.162 --> 00:12:23.535
in der heym nokhn baf- nokhn bafrayen?

00:12:21.769 --> 00:12:26.724
yo, yo, yo, yo. s'geven shkheynim vos zey hobn tsam geklibn veyst ir fun,

00:12:25.549 --> 00:12:29.913
vi alt iz geven ayer shvester az zi iz geshtorbn in Bergn Belzn, gedenkt ir?

00:12:28.603 --> 00:12:33.676
yo, ikh veys, efsher gekont zayn etlekhe in draysik yor.

00:12:35.691 --> 00:12:38.705
dos iz mayn bruder Yosi.

00:12:39.859 --> 00:12:42.249
er iz geven a gold arbeter,

00:12:43.065 --> 00:12:46.586
a a a a yingl tsu got un tsu layt.

00:12:46.710 --> 00:12:52.272
er hot fardint zeyer sheyn, er hot geholfn der mame, er hot undz ge- vos heyst geho-

00:12:52.448 --> 00:12:55.496
mir ho'mir gehat vos avektsufirn keyn Daytshnland.

00:12:55.722 --> 00:13:00.340
vos m'hot gehat hot men arayn geneyt gelter genug, ober

00:13:00.463 --> 00:13:04.338
vayl er iz nisht tsurikgekumen. in tsvey un fertsik hot iz er avek,

00:13:04.463 --> 00:13:07.641
un dray un fertsik iz gekumen a UNK,

00:13:07.641 --> 00:13:08.982
er iz nishto.

00:13:08.982 --> 00:13:13.181
di mame nebekh hot geveynt az s'geven a pakhed oystsuhern.

00:13:13.255 --> 00:13:15.631
ober m'hot zikh gornisht gekent helfn.

00:13:15.631 --> 00:13:17.028
un dos iz es.

00:13:16.832 --> 00:13:20.420
dos bild hot ir oykh gefunen in der heym nokhn bafrayen?

00:13:18.030 --> 00:13:20.842
yo, yo, yo, mit di oykhet.

00:13:20.933 --> 00:13:21.737
zikh gefunen.

00:13:22.806 --> 00:13:24.406
dos iz mayn zun,

00:13:24.291 --> 00:13:25.584
vi heyst er?

00:13:24.406 --> 00:13:26.107
Ansh- Anshi,

00:13:26.805 --> 00:13:28.824
dos iz zayn barmitsve,

00:13:28.999 --> 00:13:34.345
ikh hob zeyer biter shver tsam geshtelt di barmitsve tsu makhn, ikh hob nisht gehat fun vu,

00:13:34.345 --> 00:13:38.504
ober azoy vi s'hot zikh do gefirt, m'makht a barmitsve,

00:13:38.504 --> 00:13:40.133
far mentshn un far di,

00:13:40.133 --> 00:13:45.989
ikh hob mir geknapt di bakn zoln zayn royt un ikh hob mir gemakht a sheyner barmitsve far mayn zun.

00:13:44.878 --> 00:13:46.829
dos iz geven in velkhn yor?

00:13:45.989 --> 00:13:49.487
ikh meyn in tsvey un zekhtsik.

00:13:51.004 --> 00:13:52.466
dos iz a bild

00:13:52.607 --> 00:13:56.392
vos ikh hob gemakht nokh eyder ze'mir aroysgekumen in land arayn.

00:13:56.392 --> 00:13:59.160
iz dort ikh un mayn man,

00:13:59.160 --> 00:14:01.815
un dos yingl un dos meydele.

00:14:02.530 --> 00:14:06.186
zey zenen nokh geven kleyn ober s'hot zikh,

00:14:06.259 --> 00:14:12.260
az ikh bin gekumen do hot men mir gezogt, oy, du host gebrengt brilyantn aher, m'vet dir gebn,

00:14:12.756 --> 00:14:15.180
iz er ongekumen biz keyn Amerike.

00:14:15.456 --> 00:14:20.006
dos zent ir aroys, dos iz geven a kurtse farn aroysforn? in velkhn yor?

00:14:18.257 --> 00:14:26.520
yo, ikh meyn UNK zibn un un f- fuf- fuftsik,

00:14:26.779 --> 00:14:28.274
z- zeks,

00:14:28.753 --> 00:14:30.333
dos zi a bild,

00:14:30.627 --> 00:14:32.370
shoyn hitstert do,

00:14:32.370 --> 00:14:36.563
mayn man iz zeyer krank gevezn shoyn oyf der bild, dos iz geven

00:14:36.563 --> 00:14:43.423
vu er iz, der zun iz a khosn gevorn, mir zits'mir bay mir in MACHPESET, ikh zits oykh barn tish,

00:14:43.423 --> 00:14:48.592
un ikh veys vos, m'keyt dort epes, ober er zet nebekh zeyer shlekht oys.

00:14:48.801 --> 00:14:50.586
dos iz fun demolts.

00:14:50.586 --> 00:14:52.153
dos oykhet shoyn

00:14:53.577 --> 00:14:59.190
akht, ikh veys etlekhe un zekhtsik.

00:15:02.453 --> 00:15:03.864
dos iz a bild

00:15:04.005 --> 00:15:08.133
shoyn gemakht hitstert in etlekhe un zibetsik,

00:15:08.342 --> 00:15:10.276
tsi etlekhe un zekhtsik,

00:15:10.536 --> 00:15:12.234
iz dort mayn zun,

00:15:12.460 --> 00:15:14.698
un dos vayb Ester,

00:15:14.704 --> 00:15:17.837
un di groyse tokhter Reyzi,

00:15:17.860 --> 00:15:19.224
un di kleyne

00:15:19.224 --> 00:15:22.005
Simona, zi heyst shoyn nokh mayn man.

00:15:22.483 --> 00:15:26.999
un mayn tokhter, Esterl, un JEFFREY, Yossi.

00:15:26.972 --> 00:15:31.390
der zun mit zayn familye voynen in,

00:15:29.672 --> 00:15:32.315
in in Dalas.

00:15:31.390 --> 00:15:32.529
in Amerike.

00:15:32.529 --> 00:15:35.150
un di tokhter mit ir man mit di kinder?

00:15:34.482 --> 00:15:36.011
ne- in London.

00:15:40.405 --> 00:15:42.069
dos iz mayn zun,

00:15:42.227 --> 00:15:45.346
fun der, heysn heyst er Anshi,

00:15:42.261 --> 00:15:44.162
heysn heyst er?

00:15:45.346 --> 00:15:50.743
dos iz gemakht gevorn ven zi hot gemakht der barmitsve farn yingl.

00:15:50.918 --> 00:15:52.762
bin ikh dort gevezn,

00:15:52.762 --> 00:15:57.172
un di tokhter Ester, un ikh bin dort, dos iz fun di simkhe.

00:15:57.195 --> 00:16:01.053
iz ver shteyt, zitst ir in mitn, un ver shteyt, der zun?

00:15:58.950 --> 00:16:04.057
yo, der un di tokhter, yo mayn tokhter.

00:16:01.549 --> 00:16:02.910
un di tokhter.

00:16:03.490 --> 00:16:07.365
vi heyst zi ho'mir gezogt? Ester. dos iz gemakht gevorn ven?

00:16:06.443 --> 00:16:07.688
In London.

00:16:07.688 --> 00:16:10.942
dos iz shoyn gemakht gevorn hitstert far a tsvey yor.

00:16:11.353 --> 00:16:13.794
ven er hot gehat di barmitsve.

00:16:16.517 --> 00:16:19.869
dos iz mayn tokhter's tsvey kinder.

00:16:20.280 --> 00:16:21.354
vi heysn?

00:16:20.314 --> 00:16:22.504
dos iz fun der barmitsve.

00:16:22.504 --> 00:16:25.674
vi Shimen heyst dos yingl,

00:16:26.473 --> 00:16:29.251
er lernt zeyer shtark gut in shul.

00:16:29.258 --> 00:16:31.901
un dos meydele heyst Zisi,

00:16:32.363 --> 00:16:35.782
lernt oykh gut ober zi iz a bisele felerik, ober.

00:16:36.548 --> 00:16:40.001
got vet helfn. zey voynen in London.

00:16:37.189 --> 00:16:38.853
voynen zey in London.

00:16:45.156 --> 00:16:47.444
TODA RABA, UNK

00:16:45.188 --> 00:16:47.612
froy,

00:16:47.938 --> 00:16:49.079
Prayzler.

00:16:49.002 --> 00:16:50.804
Regina Prayzler,

00:16:50.804 --> 00:16:52.458
ikh dank aykh nokh a mol,

00:16:52.458 --> 00:16:55.374
far ayer onshtrengung un vuntsh aykh ir zolt zayn gezunt.

00:16:53.592 --> 00:16:54.362
yo,

00:16:55.009 --> 00:16:58.878
TODA RABA un ir oykh un hots a gut gebentsht nay yor!

00:16:58.878 --> 00:17:03.372
un makhts gute BUSINESS az s'zol zikh aykh glustn tsu geyn makhn.
